abstract: The bark Kilby, SMALL, from New-York for Quebec, anchored in Nantucket Roads this afternoon in consequence of trouble on board. The mate, Mr. WM. abstract: Early on Sunday morning two robbers effected an entrance into the public house of Mr. MURPHY, in Grand-street, near Barrow-street, Jersey City, and stole $160 in money. abstract: DROPPED DEAD. JAMES FISHER, (colored,) porter in the store of BENJAMIN FORE, No. 29 Moore street, dropped dead while talking to A. B. JACKSON, clerk in the store. abstract: Two lives were lost on the premises of the New-Haven Gas Company, last Saturday afternoon, under very distressing circumstances.
